Class Login

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.adactin.Mobileapphoteladactin1.base.BaseClass
      • com.adactin.Mobileapphoteladactin1.pages.Login

  • public class Login
extends com.adactin.Mobileapphoteladactin1.base.BaseClass
    Login class identifies all the elements in the Login Page. It has methods to login, click on forgot password link, click on sign up link check if login button is present, validate error messages for blank user name/password and invalid login credentials
